Natalie Anderson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natalie_Anderson 0 Natalie Jane Anderson (born 24 October 1981) is an English actress, singer and model. She is best known for her roles as Alicia Metcalfe in the ITV soap opera Emmerdale from 2010 to 2015 and Stella Davenport in the medical drama The Royal from 2005 to 2008. She also played the role of Nessarose in the London production Wicked from May 2009 to March 2010. As of 2015 she is a regular on ITV Lifestyle show This Morning.
